<h2>Were you involved in a rideshare accident? We can help!</h2>

									<p>Rideshare services like Uber and Lyft have changed how people get around, but they have also introduced new complications when accidents happen. Crashes involving rideshare vehicles can injure passengers, drivers, occupants of other cars, cyclists, and pedestrians, and the question of who is financially responsible is not always simple. AccidentLogic connects people hurt in rideshare accidents with lawyers who understand the specific rules and insurance structures that apply to these cases.</p>

